headline.main: What’s on TV Friday: ‘Fire at Sea’ and ‘Vice: Trans Youth’

lead_paragraph: Manchester City striker Sergio Aguero is determined to produce his best form in the final three months of the campaign before he holds talks on his future at the Premier League club in June.
